H. No. 1458 / 55 OG No. 38, 8108 (September 21, 1959)

[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 2540, June 21, 1959 ]

AN ACT CREATING CERTAIN BARRIOS IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF OLUTANGA, PROVINCE OF ZAMBOANGA DEL SUR.

Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Congress assembled:

SECTION 1. The following sitios in the Municipality of Olutanga, Province of Zamboanga del Sur, are converted into barrios thereof:

Sitio Baganipay to be known as the barrio of Ma lipay;

Sitio Tabian to be known as the barrio of Mercedes;

Sitio Sibayog to be known as the barrio of Salagunting;

Sitio Tandu Taba to be known as the barrio of Estancia;

Sitio Bagurod to be known as the barrio of Balasan;

Sitio Dao to be known as the barrio of Dayag; and

Sitio Cawilan Sur to be known as the barrio of Fama.

SEC. 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.

Enacted without executive approval, June 21, 1959.
